title: Mantango Attack of the Mushroom People DVDRip, Japanese Sci-Fi (
description:
Storyline 1:

Passengers of a shipwreck struggle for survival against the elements, and each other, when they find themselves stranded on a remote island, plagued with radioactive mushrooms. 
Surprisingly candid characterizations portraying the grim realities of survival, no silly or superficial heroes in this one.

Storyline 2:

A group of pleasure-seeking young people are stranded on a mysterious island when their boat crashes. One by one they succumb to the lure of the deadly mushrooms. 

2.35 Widescreen

DVDRip, MKV, H264 

Directed by Ishiro Honda. Choice of English dubbed or Japanese language audio tracks.

Optional English or Japanese subtitles.
